{"tid":614260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制圍攻戴耀廷，豈是殺雞儆猴咁簡單？","createTime":"2018-04-02T11:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T16:42:05.000Z","uid":16970,"like":129,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"55610514406d0dfc5396cb6ab7c6cb6bde23d2bd","tid":614260,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"成個建制系統點解對戴耀廷講嘅嘢咁大反應呢？<br />\n<br />\n一，因為佢係戴耀廷。姑勿論你點評鑑佢過去幾年做嘅事，晌中聯辦香港政府建制派眼中，一個由學者同中產組成嘅溫和反對派運動，係比由年青人組成嘅激進反對派運動，威脅更加大。<br />\n<br />\n二，因為佢係晌台灣講。晌香港有唔少人發表過支持香港獨立嘅言論，建制系統嘅反應都冇咁大，但今次戴教授係晌台灣發表相關言論。中共怕嘅唔係你閂埋門講到有幾激，而係你走出去同本地以外嘅人講地方獨立思潮，又或者係幾個地域嘅獨立運動連結一齊，就算幾溫和都冇情講。<br />\n<br />\n三，因為戴教授晌話香港人可以自決前途嘅條件，係中國專制統治嘅完結，依個「專制統治完結」，先係拮到中共死穴。對中共嚟講，地方獨立運動都係小打小鬧，但講到結束專制統治，就直情係要中共死，佢又點會唔大反應？<br />\n<br />\n敵人越恐懼，就更加證明方向正確。戴教授被譴責之事，只靠香港政圈同公民社會回應係杯水車薪，點樣可以同台灣政圈連結起嚟去作出反應，先係我地要考慮嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fish.flavour/posts/2032526863653824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffish.flavour%2Fposts%2F2032526863653824&d=q3o5axvosZp8FsCNA2DpAr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=7155c63c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fish.flavour/posts/2032526863653824</a>"},{"pid":"2d0da0a88c22349a2256d0ed36e0a0b16788c5b7","tid":614260,"uid":35870,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"支持戴耀廷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f780848d5b76ece7ff0ae159d1de6ca1c137da3f","tid":614260,"uid":35870,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a4f7f8cfaea797cdca75d63c8b204020bd86b9f9","tid":614260,"uid":44358,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"今次係保衛思想同言論自由，點都要撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443f5b1787d711c4aed7a61ca6270b2c714fecb9","tid":614260,"uid":16970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a4f7f8cfaea797cdca75d63c8b204020bd86b9f9","tid":614260,"uid":44358,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"今次係保衛思想同言論自由，點都要撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"得香港自己搞, 冇用架喎&hellip;"},{"pid":"08e930df6f0f10b81e65ae2656c29125a991ca32","tid":614260,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbc958f3fc675150b8acb04af90a83312500ead","tid":614260,"uid":44105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:48:23.000Z","msg":"Posh"},{"pid":"d778fdf93c9417ec280a5aa22c97fe78cd5538ad","tid":614260,"uid":16970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"嘩, 依個post好多正評喎&hellip;"},{"pid":"5a87e238a63caa4bd3da23f90762735970e8613f","tid":614260,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:24:27.000Z","msg":"再推推."},{"pid":"1dec5493e7bd0d3bde95852ffd29e8c66a586a55","tid":614260,"uid":137725,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:28:10.000Z","msg":"樓主講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正皮&gt;繼續返工&gt;加班&gt;用支那寶拎優惠&gt;LIHKG 睇反中threads &gt;正皮..."},{"pid":"7efd26439e4071fea8b9f5e8e2234516ebb4321d","tid":614260,"uid":104443,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:29:32.000Z","msg":"共匪詭計多端！當今世上萬惡之源！究竟香港嘅未來應該點樣去行？誠然港獨原意係好，而且亦係對香港人最好嘅選擇，但係共匪實在太強大，文武兼備，要五毛有五毛，要槍有槍，要炮有炮，我哋必須考慮到自己究竟有冇足夠力量成功令香港獨立，抑或只係流於理想之中，以宜家大部分香港人嘅生活水平，究竟有幾多人願意為對抗中共而犧牲自我？肯定有，但亦係少數。<br />\n<br />\n大家請睇下中華民國，由1949年失去大陸江山以嚟，仍堅守到台澎金馬至今近七十載！證明消滅共匪仲存有希望！如果台灣識做嘅話，就應該持續強化軍備，準備他日同共匪決一死戰！收復大陸河山！<br />\n<br />\n大家，都面對住共匪唔同形式嘅迫害！樓價貴，學位少，每日150腥移民，人口爆炸，以至中國人公民質素低下，全部都係共匪一手造成！共匪不擇手段意欲摧毀香港本土文化，但以宜家民主化嘅中華民國絕對冇可能做出比肩共匪嘅惡行！<br />\n<br />\n請大家支持香港回歸中華民國！匯聚全港民意向臨時首都台北之總統府請願！與其等到2047年等死，不如回歸中華民國！咁對香港亦未嘗係好選擇！況且中華民國先係正統中國，法理上中華民國亦有《南京條約》正本，絕對有權收回香港！共匪必須被消滅！我笑住睇班五毛橫屍街頭！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中華民國萬歲！<br />\n正統中國萬歲！<br />\n三民主義萭歲！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/002715_a3fa723bda0c29665bda8848c00790f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F002715_a3fa723bda0c29665bda8848c00790f7.png&h=2c89cbe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反對共匪（陸獨），反對台獨，中華民國先係中國正統！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/002812_bd33e163a9fc2e9371e158940b0fbf3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F002812_bd33e163a9fc2e9371e158940b0fbf3f.png&h=93fc6b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共匪必須被消滅！中華民國將會再次統一中國！請大家支持香港回歸中華民國！中華民國先係中國嘅未來！中華民國先係香港嘅未來！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">本人再一次請大家支持香港回歸中華民國！中華民國萬歲！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6eb7698a9504d1b50817c7e96c6c45619efefa58","tid":614260,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffee69990e634a553b609d211f2b6197b66c412","tid":614260,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"又推推."},{"pid":"dfe238914d9ec2b8b199030c93422073f0a089a1","tid":614260,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"係香港講巴塞獨立, 會比西班牙拉<br />\n<br />\n我想第一個去自首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72de289753b03101633edfd966f1da1a54b6ffb2","tid":614260,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfe238914d9ec2b8b199030c93422073f0a089a1","tid":614260,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"係香港講巴塞獨立, 會比西班牙拉<br />\n<br />\n我想第一個去自首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:58:46.000Z","msg":"乜會既咩？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb5c5a838d705dc3e157c46dbff851012c6acd1","tid":614260,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c2e4ab29882674bf57d1962354bfcff9b16be4","tid":614260,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a5ff37d3b913c32406c7422b423b180e0dfd22","tid":614260,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cd59f1ed18ee9b6f94fb6a4ac3f688fc554949","tid":614260,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民打手食魚有魚味出post</span><br />\n<br />\n非主流意見: 其實議事規則修訂唔係好大件事&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/t/498760/12?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/t/498760/12?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#1食魚有魚味 &bull; 3mo</span><br />\n<br />\n全體委員會法定人數變咗二十人, 但全體委員會審議階段發言次數不限, 基本上講幾耐都得, 直至主席剪布為止.<br />\n<br />\n呈請書門檻變做三十五人, 但呈請書根本係廢, 冇傳召證人權力, 唔會查到嘢出嚟.<br />\n<br />\n主席有權唔接受及合併議員修訂案, 相關權力而家都有.<br />\n<br />\n最大影響都係縮短表決鐘無須辯論, 中止待續議案可以無須辯論, 同某啲無需預告議案要主席批准, 但依啲只係令拉布少咗幾招, 而唔係拉唔到.<br />\n<br />\n講到天跌落嚟咁, 仲要拉埋廿三條嚟講, 就真係誇張晒.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#4 食魚有魚味 3mo</span><br />\n<br />\n冇架, 大家喊打喊殺, 有幾多人真係睇過份修訂先?<br />\n<br />\n主流就係啱嘅, 咁支持民主回歸都唔係錯呀.<br />\n4<br />\n39<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#7食魚有魚味 &bull; 33mo</span><br />\n<br />\n而家都係一樣&quot;直到主席剪布為止&quot;架喎, 你唔係覺得修訂唔過主席就唔俾剪布呀&hellip;"},{"pid":"43662dc24ad17547ebb217afffd1201821efe4ef","tid":614260,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c5c2e4ab29882674bf57d1962354bfcff9b16be4","tid":614260,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T10:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:44:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛群龍共舞<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/094417_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F094417_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4156b346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0a82c91f1f969299d2622aee0fb290b960deccaf","tid":614260,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T02:39:30.000Z","msg":"當我真心膠<br />\n我一向覺得戴耀廷鬼鬼哋，希望唔好俾我估中～～佢之後會道歉。。。。<br />\n借呢件事先攬個港獨牌頭上身，再道歉嚟判港獨死亡"},{"pid":"6e2876c83b40088ad8ab4e4765823ac35119f1c2","tid":614260,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a82c91f1f969299d2622aee0fb290b960deccaf","tid":614260,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T02:39:30.000Z","msg":"當我真心膠<br />\n我一向覺得戴耀廷鬼鬼哋，希望唔好俾我估中～～佢之後會道歉。。。。<br />\n借呢件事先攬個港獨牌頭上身，再道歉嚟判港獨死亡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"@關愛座hunter<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc28aca837a5d526e917f447b1e30a522c1ad51","tid":614260,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43662dc24ad17547ebb217afffd1201821efe4ef","tid":614260,"uid":47359,"